title: Isekai Mahou wa Okureteru! Gaiden (WN) - Novel Updates
author: Gamei Hitsuji   樋辻臥命
description: This is a story about Suimei Yakagi, the protagonist from The Other World’s Magic is too far Behind!, during his time on Earth. The magic he uses here is a bit different from the main story, but please enjoy it as a modern version specification.>
